com.hrauf.util

Class ParseDrawingVectorString

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • com.hrauf.util.ParseDrawingVectorString
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class ParseDrawingVectorString
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
    This class implements the HandlerBase helper class, which means that it defines all the "callback" methods that the SAX parser will invoke to notify the application. In this example we override the methods that we require. This code uses full package names in places to help keep the JAXP and SAX APIs distinct.
